<emphasis id="B925EAD3FD3BFFACFF18F876FF5ED4F0" bold="true" box="[226,243,1972,1996]" pageId="1" pageNumber="138">B</emphasis>
, Drone general view of the site. 
<emphasis id="B925EAD3FD3BFFACFDAEF876FDCBD4F0" bold="true" box="[596,614,1972,1996]" pageId="1" pageNumber="138">C</emphasis>
, Detailed view of the outcrop with the red arrow indicating the layers yielding amber.
</paragraph>
</caption>
